{"tid":2027903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"認清事實，其實對家一早就知國安法","createTime":"2020-05-21T14:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T09:57:12.000Z","uid":313468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf15c4e740b403758f2916efdc0f8a45af5c2160","tid":2027903,"uid":313468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqPq3VL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqPq3VL.png&h=6c9e0e1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實河妖尋日已經講過<br />\n<br />\n所有行動出左文宣，係TG傳，用得TG嘅人都係我地班teenage <br />\n<br />\n咁上左年紀嘅和理非呢？無用TG嘅上班族呢？<br />\n宜家就星期五，我希望大家幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n文宣組可以將國安法，即23條嘅壞處整文宣，連同黎緊嘅行動，例如星期日嘅遊行，係同一張A4 size 嘅圖出，咁貼嘅行動組可以方便啲<br />\n<br />\n文宣唔可以淨係講自己人，要教育埋一班中立，高收入，藍嘅人<br />\n所以表示23條壞處嘅文宣要多<br />\n<br />\n另外Social media<br />\n我好記得，616，818，唔同嘅朋友會畫一幅連狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再寫818or 616，再tag 5個人<br />\n呢幾日，係時候玩翻呢個Challenge，去叫更多人出<br />\n<br />\nFB，有班和理非，有好多黃嘅group ，黃色經濟圈，一啲地區性嘅街坊group，可以搵人將TG channel嘅行動文宣圖share上去，再叫人share <br />\n<br />\n另外黃店，除左memo<br />\n行動嘅文宣希望可以每日門口貼住，比班和理非知到，另外可以整埋QR code，scan完係條link，比一班未有TG 嘅人down同follow 日程channel<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家對家擺明係想知我地呢幾日會有乜行動<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"fce0d5495bbdd66cf8b123e519ddad10f6528628","tid":2027903,"uid":313468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a2d316077a75202610c840ca6956a5d66a2b9d2","tid":2027903,"uid":313468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0deb28ea7e3c9bc88d10cb7ce97a626552c1c1","tid":2027903,"uid":313468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f402c695b9dbe0d1970af4d695e210cbed9e87","tid":2027903,"uid":313468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c